<tr class="even areaheader  firstrow"><td colspan="2"><span class="courselistcomment areaheader ">Courses</span></td><td class="hourscol"></td></tr>
<tr class="odd lastrow"><td colspan="2"><span class="courselistcomment">12 hours of 300- or 400-level CBA courses.</span></td><td class="hourscol">12</td></tr>
<tr class="listsum"><td colspan="2">Total Hours</td><td class="hourscol">12</td></tr></tbody>
</table>

<p>A course can be used to satisfy only one area of required or elective courses.</p>
